    {
      "id": "1ac4750c-f3ba-802a-989c-cbb7794cdf00",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The authors propose a new recommender system for learning activities that uses knowledge graphs. The model uses student-learning activity graph to identify common learning activity pathways.  Authors test their approach in an ITS on the teaching of Java.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1ac4750c-f3ba-802a-989c-cbb7794cdf00",
